  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigator will perform clinical studies to test the hypothsis that participants who
      had Alzhemer's disease will have different gut microbiota in the feaces as compared to
      participants who did not have Alzhemer's disease, as well as compared to their spouse.The
      investigators plan to perfoem the studies in 150 participants in Shanghai Tenth's People's
      Hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
